com.here.mobility.sdk.map

Class PolylineOverlay

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.mobility.sdk.map.geometry.GeometryOverlay
      • com.here.mobility.sdk.map.PolylineOverlay

  • public final class PolylineOverlay
extends GeometryOverlay
    A styled polyline that can be added to the map via MapController.addPolyline(PolylineOverlay). The polyline style contains color and width values.
